---
<<bg bg_supervisoroffice>>

Arthur returns—his son lost the debate.

Arthur: Still here. No fire alarms, no legal pings, no emails with "URGENT" in all caps. I'll take it.

Player: How was the debate?

Arthur: He lost. Blamed "institutional bias against niche anime references." I suggested maybe next time he could cite sources that aren't from a show about sword-fighting teenagers. He said I "don't understand rhetoric." He's fourteen.

Player: Sounds like he's got a future in this industry.

Arthur: Don't. I'm not ready for that thought.

He pulls up your dashboard. Engagement and Sanity lines from last night glow on the wall screen.

<<if $r1_d1_strategy == "gentle_landing">>
