Arthur: It's... unusual. Most new leads panic-optimize for engagement because that's the number with the trophy next to it. You went the other direction. Leadership will have opinions. I'll try to make sure they're quiet ones.
<<set $trust_supervisor -= 1>>
<<elseif $r1_d1_strategy == "study_adjacent">>
Arthur: Engagement steady, sanity steady, he might actually know what a supply curve is now. Balanced. Boring. In this context, boring is a compliment.

